{"tid":2000272,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[An App] [Bug Report] 嚴重SelectableText Bug","createTime":"2020-05-03T18:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T18:53:46.000Z","uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e1198a30c30d419c2122bd952642ce77f8b1e9","tid":2000272,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"Reproducible steps:<br />\n<br />\n1. 開Editor （回po/開po嗰嚿嘢）<br />\n2. Select任何含有Icon嘅Text（淨係得Icon都得）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如Select以下呢段<br />\nTEXTWITHICONFROMLIHKG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住要開咗Editor先Select<br />\n你可以Quote我然後編輯我Quote嘅嘢<br />\n又或者自己打粒Icon再Select<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 撳任何一個位 取消個Selection(唔取消都得)<br />\n4. 喺任何地方Copy任何Text (LIHKG 以外都得)<br />\n5. Paste下 睇下你Copy咗啲乜<br />\n6. 再試下周圍Copy&amp;Paste or Cut&amp;Paste<br />\n<br />\nSimple fixes:<br />\nForce close LIHKG 或<br />\nPop走個Editor (即係撳Back掣/左上角嗰粒)<br />\n<br />\n有時間不妨試下 睇下係咪淨係得我係咁"},{"pid":"ca1ab477e4c334a4024736ba57b23ec3d86e1f1b","tid":2000272,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"呢個Bug最惡毒係<br />\n會影響到成個系統嘅Clipboard<br />\n又好難諗到 究竟係邊隻App 邊個位出事<br />\n<br />\n機緣巧合<br />\n終於俾我搵到點解我個Clipboard出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4983c74be306d7bff7aa7f1a35cf49381b3ee5d","tid":2000272,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:07:46.000Z","msg":"BTW 點解依家淨係打標題 冇打內文<br />\n再Pop出去 又唔幫我Save低返個草稿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1c16b8df0441a3f827ae3d3d6d4011ac67323f","tid":2000272,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:13:27.000Z","msg":"更正：<br />\n直接Quote我 然後編輯我打嘅嘢<br />\n<strong>係冇用嘅</strong><br />\n因為粒Icon會變返做 iconCode: <code>:o)</code><br />\n<br />\n總之要自己打粒Icon再Select<br />\n<br />\nQuote我然後編輯唔係唔得<br />\n但要人手喺Icon list撳返粒Icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入去 Editor度"},{"pid":"c21ee9ad53efa7c0725b881b31ca16aef90b5818","tid":2000272,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:13:58.000Z","msg":"標題應該係Editor Bug先啱<br />\n普通SelectableRichText冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96eecb496971c7efb347b8b6a2c551bf977fe3b4","tid":2000272,"uid":179338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"介唔介意錄一錄影做一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270fcbec0b764a7474cd61bd9682db4342e4aa97","tid":2000272,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"96eecb496971c7efb347b8b6a2c551bf977fe3b4","tid":2000272,"uid":179338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"介唔介意錄一錄影做一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時頒返個大蓮燈勳章俾我"},{"pid":"dc14b7c093b3f3770fac007714c9456bc0cabbac","tid":2000272,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"App以外都會出事<br />\n嗰啲位我唔錄了"},{"pid":"3a62aa1eb5cc24e4ed4ac695db9e16ac1bc005ff","tid":2000272,"uid":179338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc14b7c093b3f3770fac007714c9456bc0cabbac","tid":2000272,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"App以外都會出事<br />\n嗰啲位我唔錄了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明 下version 會fix"},{"pid":"9e3bc5b66ace5ba7737c6fd37590356aadf783ed","tid":2000272,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a62aa1eb5cc24e4ed4ac695db9e16ac1bc005ff","tid":2000272,"uid":179338,"